<doc id="617351" wikidata="Q348272" url="?curid=617351" title="Hopkinton">
<text>Hopkinton is the name of several places in the United States:

* Hopkinton, Iowa
* Hopkinton, Massachusetts, a New England town
** Hopkinton (CDP), Massachusetts, the main village in the town
* Hopkinton, New Hampshire
* Hopkinton, New York
* Hopkinton, Rhode Island, a New England town
** Hopkinton (CDP), Rhode Island, a village in the town</text><links>
