<text>Savolax (&quot;Savo&quot;) is the Swedish language name of a geographical region in Finland which can refer to:

*Savolax - a historical Province of Sweden
*Norra Savolax landskap - a current Region of Finland
*Södra Savolax landskap - a current Region of Finland
*Eastern Finland - Province of Finland 1997-2010</text><links>
